{"article_id":"beafdD0G3YXaeUMf","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"NEW YORK","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"( AP ) -","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"Facebook is giving its privacy tools a makeover","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"as it reels from criticisms over its data practices","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"and faces tighter European regulations in the coming months .","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"The changes won ' t affect Facebook ' s privacy policies or the types of data","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"it gathers on users .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"But the company hopes","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"its 2.2 billion users will have an easier time","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"navigating its complex and often confusing privacy and security settings .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"Facebook says","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"it also wants to give users a simpler way","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"to access and download the data","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"it collects on them .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"Wednesday ' s announcement follows revelations","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"that a Trump-affiliated consulting firm , Cambridge Analytica , got data on millions of Facebook users .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"That included information on friends of people","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"who had downloaded a psychological quiz app ,","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"even though those friends hadn ' t given explicit consent","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"to sharing .","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"In addition , Facebook is also facing widespread criticism","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"for collecting years of contact names , telephone numbers and call and text histories from Android users .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"The company has not said exactly","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"what it used such data for or why it needed it .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"On Monday , the Federal Trade Commission said","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"it is investigating Facebook over its privacy practices .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Facebook ' s chief privacy officer , Erin Egan , said in a blog post","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"that most of the privacy updates have been in the works for \" some time ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"but the events of the past several days underscore their importance . \"","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"Facebook also said","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"it plans to update its privacy policy and terms of service in the coming weeks ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"but gave no further details .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"The company has tried over the years to simplify its privacy settings ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"yet the controls remain hard to find and use for many people .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"For example , Facebook announced in 2009","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"that it was consolidating six privacy pages and more than 30 settings on to a single privacy page .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Yet mobile users still had to go to nearly 20 different places","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"to access all of their privacy controls .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"Now , Facebook says","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"they will be accessible from a single place .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"Facebook says","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"it is also adding \" clearer explanations \"","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"about how its privacy controls work .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"Chris Cox , Facebook ' s chief product officer , called the new settings \" the first of many steps \"","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"the company is taking","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"to address privacy concerns .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"Facebook has been working on the changes in preparation for the European Union ' s General Data Protection Regulation ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"which were approved two years ago","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"and take effect May 25 .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"The rules are designed","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"to make it easier for consumers to give and withdraw consent for the use of their data .","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"They apply to any company","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"that collects data on EU residents ,","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"no matter where it is based .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"To comply with this ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Facebook is adding a section","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"called \" access your information , \" a secure way for users to manage data","depth":14},{"id":57,"text":"they ' ve shared with the company ,","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"including status updates , comments and things","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"they have searched for .","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"That ' s where people can go","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"to delete information","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"or download a copy .","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"While this download was already possible ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"it took some time","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"to figure out how to do it .","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"Cox said","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"the changes let people browse through their information in detail ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"without having to download it .","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"For example , users will now be able to look up a post from a specific date in the past .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Cox said","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"while the changes are \" in line with the principle of GDPR ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"\" there ' s also a \" bunch of stuff","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"that goes above and beyond that . \"","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"Facebook also said","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"it will propose updates to its terms of service in the coming weeks","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"and update its privacy policy ,","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"but gave no further details .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":157,"left":0,"right":156,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":156,"left":1